00:24:37,690 --> 00:24:39,270
Budem si dávať pozor.

324
00:24:51,370 --> 00:24:56,580
Danny, dorazil si včera v poriadku?

325
00:24:57,510 --> 00:25:00,510
Nie je mi s tebou nepríjemne.

326
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:02,260
Bože.

327
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:05,230
