342
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:00,480
Počkať.

343
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,770
Trafila som?

344
00:26:03,770 --> 00:26:04,940
Neverím.

345
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:07,410
