Počúvam.

350
00:26:24,930 --> 00:26:26,570
Poď za mnou von.

351
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:28,410
Som pred tvojím bytom.

352
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:35,580
Čo je?

353
00:26:36,710 --> 00:26:39,250
Tú párty neusporiadame.

354
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:42,390
