360
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:07,080
Aj včera si bola krutá.

361
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,880
Máš pravdu.

362
00:27:10,470 --> 00:27:14,050
Chcela som to spraviť, aby ma otec uznal.

363
00:27:15,010 --> 00:27:17,460
Nikdy sa o mňa nezaujímal,

364
00:27:17,850 --> 00:27:20,660
