455
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:22,820
Nie.

456
00:34:24,270 --> 00:34:26,490
Aj na to som už našla odpoveď.

457
00:34:31,310 --> 00:34:34,250
Nepila by som kávu z mužom...

458
00:34:34,250 --> 00:34:36,760
o ktorého nemám záujem.

459
00:34:40,890 --> 00:34:42,400
Takže...

460
00:34:43,160 --> 00:34:44,640
chceš...

461
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:48,110
Áno.

462
00:34:49,030 --> 00:34:50,740
Spravme to.

463
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:54,780
Batériu lásky.

464
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:13,000
