470
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:42,960
Trvám na tom.

471
00:35:43,850 --> 00:35:45,230
Spravme to.

472
00:35:49,230 --> 00:35:51,270
Bolo ti kvôli Seo Tae Hyunovi nepríjemne.

473
00:35:54,730 --> 00:35:57,980
